column5: Hi all,  Gauranteed way to get snow is to say the word 'boat' in March!     Went for a drive looking for some open water yesterday........found some at Eagle Lake                  As soon as i got home i called my buddy Cliff to say 'GET THE BOAT READY!' We headed back today to cast from shore, with half a foot of snow on the ground!!!! Roloff got his first taste of fishing open water....he likes it!          <iframe width="560" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/7oehDYylrsI" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
Your dog looks like he's about ready to take a bite out of that walleye.
Is that the narrows that is Bear??
Awesome!  My lab used to drag 20 + lb pound chinook out of small streams by their back.  Now he won't even so much as acknowledge a fish.
